      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Zyno是内容CDN，但GradeSync和StudentDB的关系我有点模糊——GradeSync是业务动作还是系统模块？另外，用户第一步是选择persona和phase，这个直接连到Frontend对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zyno (Education_ContentCDN)",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "User",
        "Frontend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用户先选persona/phase，直接和Frontend交互。GradeSync是业务标识，API v1收到请求后会去Zyno做编排（Orchestrate），Zyno内部会查StudentDB拿到学生数据，然后返回JourneyStepResponse。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (Education_ContentCDN)",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "JourneyStepResponse"
