    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：User到Frontend是选择操作，Frontend用POST /journeys/{Education_GradeSync}/step调用API v1，然后API v1发Orchestrate给Zyno。Zyno回JourneyStepResponse，这里带StudentDB的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
