      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Zyno回给API的响应要标清楚是虚线返回，因为那是异步回调或者内部查询后的结果。然后API v1要把ui_blocks和next_state一起返回给Frontend，最后Frontend渲染给用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zyno (Education_ContentCDN)",
