      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整：Zyno到API v1用了虚线箭头，标注JourneyStepResponse。API v1到Frontend也是虚线返回，带ui_blocks和next_state。最后Frontend到User是渲染交互。您看Zyno的别名写成Education_ContentCDN可以吗？",
